Principles of visual communication. Design principles. Different tools according to the purpose. Graphical visualization. Visual self-expression skills. Typography. Information design and presentation.Objectives/eesmärkid:  The aim of the course is to provide knowledge of the principles of visual communication and graphic design and their application aspects on the example of web-based or freeware programs.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  Upon the completion of the course the student: 1) know the principles of communication design; 2) know and be able to apply visualization techniques; 4) be able to select between different tools according to the purpose; 5) understand the principles of information design and presentation and be able to apply them according to the purpose.
